Title: An Act Changing the Name of Lanao General Hospital in Marawi City to Amai Pakpak General Hospital
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 115
An Act Changing the Name of Lanao General Hospital in Marawi City to Amai Pakpak General Hospital
Section 1. The name of Lanao General Hospital in Marawi City is hereby changed to Amai Pakpak General Hospital.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: January 21, 1981
